{"tid":1649884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後邊個搞抗爭嘉年華食抗爭蛋糕就係鬼！","createTime":"2019-10-12T18:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T00:49:13.000Z","uid":188871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f58c7a215e4ac9ada76df78f315ce5d467bda72e","tid":1649884,"uid":188871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:53:11.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n睇到有人拎蛋糕去太子慶祝<br />\n真係嬲撚到出煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LhDb2Jj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhDb2Jj.jpg&h=374e1fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚明顯你地已經有哂地方俾你食蛋糕切蛋糕<br />\n點解仲要特登拎落去太子站切蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0kN0V3J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0kN0V3J.jpg&h=fd816e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係囉 你實冇預過啦<br />\n全部story都係你自己出咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全係宜家的你打倒幾個鐘之前的你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完真係有一刻衝動想棄驚掉裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後睇到連登有人留言話我地咁易就割席棄驚<br />\n容乜易之後d狗照板煮碗搵卧底出嚟又切蛋糕激我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有見及此 我正式宣布</span></span><br />\n以後邊個再喺抗爭時候慶祝生日 打乒乓波 打邊爐<br />\n嗰個就係鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗同我解釋咁多<br />\n以後見一個獅鳥一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大家喺適當時候做適當嘅野<br />\n唔係話唔俾你生日<br />\n但係真係睇場合啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真 如果真係同路人 手足<br />\n咁啱生日 咪順便當係放自己一日假 好好抖下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都辛苦喇 堅持左四個幾月喇<br />\n大家都係叻叻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔會放棄咖，你呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後 聽日 10.13 十八區 遍地開花</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2Ue0x6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2Ue0x6.jpg&h=bca62409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8819a8bc1c993bc9a057e066d6ff5adf287056","tid":1649884,"uid":188871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:58:30.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5531e5f5217316a935ecd128ea79a16f8e96424","tid":1649884,"uid":188871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEtn9xN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEtn9xN.png&h=3afa45b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a27ce63c64b6a28589db451f1cbb9fb8aa218747","tid":1649884,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:21:10.000Z","msg":"不篤灰 不割蓆唔係口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMrUgfE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt